data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Steele Creek, Charlotte! This 4BR, 3BA gem seamlessly combines elegance & functionality. The main level boasts a bedroom, formal dining, and a spacious eat-in kitchen opening to the great room. The backyard, on 1/3 acre lot, invites your personal touch with a rear outdoor living area and playground. Upstairs, the primary suite is a luxurious retreat with a separate tub and shower, providing a spa-like experience. The upper level also features two well-appointed bedrooms, a full bath, and a versatile bonus room—ideal for a media room, home gym, or playroom. Convenience meets style with the laundry room strategically located on the upper level. Imagine hosting barbecues, enjoying al fresco dining, or simply relaxing in your private outdoor haven. The playground ensures endless fun for all. Your dream lifestyle begins here. Seize the opportunity to call this treasure your own. Home Warranty provided & Ring Doorbell to convey.
